=Description=

Petros:

"Spitharians live in a small set of stacked sea cargo containers, with the more luxurious add-on in the form of couple camping trailers. Around ten adults, one little girl, dogs and cats – the whole minature community. In the very beginning of their history.

They are living on someone elses ground, in the semi arid country of red clay soil, hot in the day and damn cold in the night. Harsh conditions for everyone. And this is their second year here."
(http://expeditionfreedom.org/2013/06/12/the-red-earth-tribe/)


